import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const UserForm = styled.form`
    display: flex;
`

export default function SignUp() {
  return (
    <UserForm>
        <label htmlFor="firstName" name="firstName" id="firstName" required>First Name</label>
        <input type="text" />
        <label htmlFor="lastName" name="lastName" id="lastName" required>Last Name</label>
        <input type="text" />
        <label for="email">Enter your email: </label>
        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" required />
    </UserForm>
  )
}
